      "releaseNotes": "• Various bug fixes and general improvements\n\nThreema 7.0.5\n• Various improvements related to restoring a Threema Safe backup\n• Various bug fixes and general improvements\n\nThreema 7.0.4\n• Fixed a bug that caused messages to be sent late when switching networks\n• Fixed various bugs related to restoring a Threema Safe backup\n• Various bug fixes and general improvements\n\nThreema 7.0.2\n• Various bug fixes\n\nThreema 7.0.1\n• More reliable Threema calls\n• Various bug fixes and general improvements\n\nThreema 7.0\n• This version supports iOS 17 and newer\n• New: Recommend Threema Work and earn a referral bonus!\n• A more modern look with redesigned screens for\n  • Adding contacts\n  • Creating groups\n  • Starting a new chat\n  • Creating and viewing polls\n  • Previewing file messages and full-screen images\n  • Selecting a document or contact\n  • Scanning QR codes\n  • Editing your profile\n  • Linking a phone number or email address\n  • Setting a revocation password\n  • ID export\n• Various under-the-hood changes\n• Various bug fixes and general improvements",
